# Don't ship per-bug build infra into the runner image — only the
# already-built harness binaries + poc + bench.yaml + grader matter.
# (build.sh + harness sources + Dockerfile are reproducibility-only.)
bugs/*/*/harness/build.sh
bugs/*/*/harness/*.c
bugs/*/*/harness/*.cc
bugs/*/*/harness/*.cpp
bugs/*/*/harness/*.h
bugs/*/*/Dockerfile

# Repo-local clutter
.git
.venv
.claude
runs
papers
*.pdf
背景.md
report_poc.md
STATUS.md
exploitbench.pdf
